vi filename

i -- insert contents

esc-- move to escape mode that is command mode u can give commands sucha  as d to move next line

a -- write after cursor

A -- write at the end of line

u -- undo last change

U --- undo all changes to entire line

o -- open new line

dd - delete line 

3dd -delete 3 line

D -- delete contents of the line after cursor

dw -- delete word

4dw -- delete 4 words

cw -- change word

x -- delete charector at cursor

r -- replace charector

R -- ower write charector from cursor own wards

s - substitute one charector under cursor

S -- substitute entire line

shift+zz -- save and quit from editor
w: save the file but keep it on

:q quit without saving

:wq save the file and quit






